ComicInfo.Summary: After being held captive and raped by multiple men, Alice escapes and runs for safety. In her hurry she tumbles off a cliff and awakens in some bushes at the bottom unharmed. There a girl with rabbit ears and a large pocket watch hanging around her neck, Bunny, greets her. She sniffs Alice and tells her that they smells the same, meaning Alice is invited to her kingdom. Alice follows the girl into a hole in the cliff face where she falls a great distance. During the fall Alice observes the lust-scape, which arouses her and thus provokes the the sex walls to attack. They capture Alice and sexually assault her till she orgasms twice while considering the wall's surprising gentleness. Then they release her and Alice falls, exhausted, to the bottom of the rabbit hole. There Bunny helps her up and leads her towards an exit.
